// concurrency.nv — async/await, channels, goroutines, structured concurrency
//
// Demonstrates: async fn, await, spawn, go (goroutines), Channel<T>,
// select, WaitGroup, Mutex, and common concurrent patterns.
//
// STATUS: Compiles and runs (Phase 1 sync portion only).
//   async/await codegen and the channel runtime are Phase 2.
//   All async declarations are commented out below.
//   The runnable demo at the bottom shows sync patterns that work today.
//   nv run examples/concurrency.nv

module examples.concurrency

